| **DI** | Hilt |
| **Network** | OkHttp (TLS self-signed to Bridge) |
| **Annotation** | KSP |
| **Architecture** | Modular (:app, :domain, :data) |
| **Bridge** | HTTPS port 8922, SSE streaming |
