## Layers

| Layer | File | Priority | Description |
|-------|------|----------|-------------|
| Domain | @include domain/entities.acm | HIGH | 13 screens, ViewModels, domain models |
| Infrastructure | @include infrastructure/repositories.acm | MEDIUM | Bridge client, OTA, auth, notifications |
| API | @include api/controllers.acm | MEDIUM | Navigation, activities, deep links |

## Module Structure

```
:app        → MainActivity, SaviaApp, Navigation, DI modules
:domain     → Models, UseCases (planned)
:data       → Bridge API, repositories (planned)
```

## 13 Screens

Home, Chat, Commands, Profile, Kanban, Approvals,
Capture, TimeLog, Dashboard, Settings, TeamManagement,
GitConfig, CompanyProfile

## Key Patterns

- Single Activity + Compose Navigation
- Hilt for DI (@HiltViewModel, @AndroidEntryPoint)
- Bridge connection: OkHttp with self-signed TLS trust
- SSE streaming for chat (chunked transfer encoding)
- OTA updates via Bridge endpoints
- APK auto-publish to ~/.savia/bridge/apk/ and scripts/dist/

## Build

- NEVER use assembleDebug directly
- Use: `./gradlew buildAndPublish` (tests → build → publish)
- JAVA_HOME=/snap/android-studio/209/jbr
- ANDROID_HOME=/home/monica/Android/Sdk
